title: Trump barely mentions Jan. 6 on third anniversary of assault on the Capitol
description: Former President Donald Trump barely mentioned the Jan. 6 assault on the Capitol as he rallied supporters in Iowa on Saturday.

title: NRA civil trial threatens to shake up gun rights organization even with leader’s resignation
description: Wayne LaPierre’s civil trial, slated to begin Monday in New York, still threatens to unravel the National Rifle Association, despite the longtime leader’s resignation from the prominent gun rights group that has held much power in the U.S. for decades.

title: Nikki Haley criticizes Trump for not debating, accusing him of 'acting like Biden'
description: Nikki Haley criticizes Trump for not debating, accusing him of 'acting like Biden'

title: A tense new Jan. 6 video shows Republican congressmen admonishing rioters trying to enter House chamber
description: Dramatic, newly released video shot by a Jan. 6 rioter shows the confrontation between two Republican members of Congress and Capitol rioters trying to breach the main door into the chamber of the U.S.

title: Visa using AI to protect credit card users from hackers
description: At Visa’s command center in Virginia, they monitor 76,000 transactions a second across more than 200 countries, facing off against hackers and fraudsters determined to steal money. The technology is powered by artificial intelligence. NBC News’ Tom Costello visited the center and explains more.
